snippet: Top-ranked Serena Williams was ousted Tuesday from the Family Circle Cup in Charleston, S.C., shocked in straight sets by No. 78 Jana Cepelova of Slovakia, 6-4, 6-4.
abstract: Jana Cepelova of Slovakia upsets Serena Williams, ousting her from the Family Circle Cup in Charleston, SC.
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Serena Williams was ousted Tuesday from the Family Circle Cup in Charleston, S.C., shocked in straight sets by No. 78 Jana Cepelova of Slovakia, 6-4, 6-4.
